{"title":"迎春会","authors":["丁志文"],"dates":[{"year":1965,"month":2,"day":22}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"迎春会"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"丁志文"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"采煤区的迎春会上，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"干部、工人聚一堂。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"青年人眉飞色舞，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"老年人喜气洋洋。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"论收获，话家常，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"讲形势，谈理想。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"歌声响，笑声扬，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"人们心里充满了春光！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"幸福象蜜糖，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"心头甜，嗓子痒，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"怎能不讲一讲？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我呀，话语儿象小河，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"顺嘴儿流淌："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“去年，干得还不坏，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"立功、受奖，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"这生活啊，实在棒！路，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"又平坦，又宽广，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"走起来，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"好象胁下生翅膀！”"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我说得得意洋洋，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"师傅却一声不响。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"怪不怪，他望着我，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一劲儿沉思默想。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"师傅哇，想什么？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"说一说吧，讲一讲。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"师傅深沉地盯着我："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“年青人，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你可知春风未来前，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"遍地是冰霜。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"也许哟，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在这欢乐的时刻，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"讲过去有点不太相当，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"但是啊！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"不经过暴虐的严冬，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"怎会爱惜温煦的春光！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"二十年前过新年，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我们披麻袋，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"团团围在火炉旁。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一块橡子面窝窝头，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"半碗发霉的土豆汤，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"填不满空瘪的肚肠！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"把头来催班，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"挥鞭舞棒，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"哪管你腹内饥饿，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"遍身创伤，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"还得把班上！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"那时节——"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"迎春春不来，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"盼天天不亮，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"矿工血泪如海洋！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"就是今天呀，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"全世界还有许多工人弟兄，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"和我们从前一样，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在殖民主义统治的国土上，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"有多少阶级兄弟盼解放。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我们不能只陶醉在幸福里，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"把他们忘，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"工人的心里，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"要把整个世界装！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"道路也并不都这样平坦，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"前面还有礁石，有风浪，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"年青人，这些你可曾想？”"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"师傅说得好啊，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"象盏灯把我心照亮。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"眼光啊，望到全世界，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"肩上啊，增加了分量，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"多么艰巨而光荣的任务，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"要我们承当！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"万不能呵万不能"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"晕倒在成绩的软床上。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"干，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"鼓干劲，心雄志壮。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"向前进，气宇轩昂。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"用手中锨镐肩上枪，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"支援全世界阶级弟兄斗争解放。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"手挽手啊臂膀靠臂膀，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"把反帝的烈火燃得更旺，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"把黑暗的旧世界埋葬！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"那时节，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"再开世界迎春会，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"迎那无限美好的春光！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"〔选自《本溪矿工报》〕"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":6,"page_end":6}